nodes.text: Galactic Republic Customs of Coruscant was a Galactic Republic law enforcement agency that enforced customs on the planet Coruscant during the Clone Wars using customs droids.

Galactic Republic Customs of Coruscant first appeared in "Lethal Trackdown," the twenty-second episode of the canon animated series Star Wars: The Clone Wars' second season, which originally aired on April 30, 2010.
